metadata.name: African King: Zulu
metadata.description:
Shaka Zulu is the King of the Zulu Kingdom in South Africa. 
Leopards are considered the king of all predators therefore only person fit to wear a Leopard skin is the man elevated to a status of a King.
Shield is a symbol of protection.
Spear is for hunting.
Feathers signifies wisdom. 
The claw necklace signifies bravery.
The breastplate is for protection.
